! 自动安装

执行以下命令：

```
bash -c "$(curl --fail --show-error --silent --location https://raw.githubusercontent.com/zdharma-continuum/zinit/HEAD/scripts/install.sh)"
```

```
代理链接
sh -c "$(curl -fsSL https://git.io/zinit-install)"
```

上述安装命令默认将[[zinit]]安装到 `~/.local/share/zinit/zinit.git`

`~/.zshrc` 文件会被更新，以及添加的三行代码分别是：`sourcing zinit.zsh` 和为 `zinit` 命令设置自动补全。

`sourcing zinit.zsh` 的意思是在 `.zshrc` 文件中添加一行代码，使得 `zinit` 在启动时被加载。

为 `zinit` 命令设置自动补全的意思是在 `.zshrc` 文件中添加两行代码，使得在使用 `zinit` 命令时可以自动补全命令。

!! 在安装过程中会提示是否安装推荐的插件，输入`n`不安装

```
🚧WARNING: /root/.zshrc already contains zinit commands. Not making any changes.
 Would you like to add 4 useful plugins - the most useful annexes (Zinit extensions that add new functions-features to the plugin manager) to the zshrc as well? It will be the following snippet:

# Load a few important annexes, without Turbo
# (this is currently required for annexes)
zinit light-mode for \
    zdharma-continuum/zinit-annex-as-monitor \
    zdharma-continuum/zinit-annex-bin-gem-node \
    zdharma-continuum/zinit-annex-patch-dl \
    zdharma-continuum/zinit-annex-rust

Enter y/n and press Return: n
```

!!! 安装完成后重启终端进入`zsh`后使用`zinit zstatus`测试[[zinit]]是否安装成功
